":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NONE"},{"text":":","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in this case the page has a pre-determined physical size and we want to stretch the image to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fit the page in one of the ways described by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"text":". The image DPI is automatically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calculated for each image from the given physical page size, page fit setting and image","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dimensions. There are two sub-cases to consider:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a. ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resamplingMethod"},{"text":" is NONE OR the calculated DPI is less than or equal to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"text":":","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in this case the image is added to the PDF without resampling, which means that the image","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"rectangle is simply rescaled to fit into the page as specified by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageSize"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"b. ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resamplingMethod"},{"text":" is not NONE AND the calculated DPI is greater than ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"text":":","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in this case the bitmap of the image is resampled to match ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"text":" using the selected method","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"before adding it to the PDF. This will result in a bitmap that is smaller than the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text